![166.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1614183491707-6CBJRG81JRRFVQYFEHF5/166.jpg)

Valentine's Day 2021 has come and gone, but there seems to still be some love in the air! In a celebration of the diverse forms love can take, DC Comics decided to release '**Love Is A Battlefield**', an 80-Page/ 10-story anthology series following specific DC characters on the most romantic of days. Join us as we discuss the "friendzone", talk gender roles and give our ideas of what other couples could have been included in this Valentine's Day Hangover Edition of the Major Issues Podcast!

**Please** leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
